<item>
            <title>[LU-12546] add option to abort recovery between MDTs but not between client/MDT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12546</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If there be some problem during recovery between MDTs, it could not affect the client&lt;br/&gt;
and the MDT, there should be some option in &quot;lctl abort_recovery&quot; to abort the recovery&lt;br/&gt;
between MDTs but don&apos;t affect the recovery between client/MDT&lt;/p&gt;</description>
